On my win 8.1 I was able to download 4.05 without problem with the Norton antivirus already running in a Toshiba satellite notebook but on 4.06 Norton did not allow me to download it and proceeded to erase the download file, then I downloaded it again and in options I forced Norton to download it and to stop prompting me problems from the classic Shell website.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3416">classicshelltavo1</a> — Sun Apr 06, 2014 3:00 pm</p><hr />
